items.title: Cruz control: Seattle wins 3rd straight over Texas
items.summary: The Mariners have been waiting for the return of some injured pitchers, but welcomed the arrival of some healthy hitting as well on Thursday as they rolled to a 10-4 win, their third straight blowout of the Rangers.
